long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
NotedIt redefines searching by providing an engine with a convenient shortcut access to your notes.

By clicking “Add to Chrome”, you accept and agree to install the NotedIt extension, set the Chrome™ default search to NotedIt, and to the Terms of Use, and Privacy Policy.

Terms of Use: https://www.noted-it.com/terms-of-use
Privacy Policy: https://www.noted-it.com/privacy-policy

Search for “notedit” in the address bar and discover your notes!
